  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SDDL
    Simple DDL (data description language) first: register your classes then: register variables then: use SDDL.create("myClass { id:1234, myDate:$myVar.aProperty } > resultVarName") after that: be happy restrictions: registered classes must have noargs-constructor there must be a oneArg setter for properties the type of the property must have a String-Constructor
